[
  {
    "text": "Why's it tough for anyone to see?",
    "start": 12.99,
    "end": 14.36,
    "scene": "desk",
    "big": false
  },
  {
    "text": "This isn't some grand philosophy.",
    "start": 14.29,
    "end": 16.67,
    "scene": "desk",
    "big": false
  },
  {
    "text": "Words tossed fast like broken debris,",
    "start": 17.17,
    "end": 19.77,
    "scene": "desk",
    "big": false
  },
  {
    "text": "Knocking the calm right outta the day.",
    "start": 20.07,
    "end": 21.87,
    "scene": "desk",
    "big": false
  },
  {
    "text": "Said something reckless—five minutes prior,",
    "start": 21.97,
    "end": 24.18,
    "scene": "neon",
    "big": false
  },
  {
    "text": "Now flames rise higher like a midnight fryer.",
    "start": 24.09,
    "end": 26.93,
    "scene": "neon",
    "big": false
  },
  {
    "text": "Thoughts keep spinning in a busted dryer,",
    "start": 27.35,
    "end": 29.84,
    "scene": "neon",
    "big": false
  },
  {
    "text": "Wish somebody'd speak straight for once, okay?",
    "start": 29.75,
    "end": 32.31,
    "scene": "neon",
    "big": false
  },
  {
    "text": "Talking circles like a worn-out tire,",
    "start": 33.93,
    "end": 35.74,
    "scene": "vortex",
    "big": false
  },
  {
    "text": "Messing with timing like a novice liar.",
    "start": 35.67,
    "end": 36.63,
    "scene": "vortex",
    "big": false
  },
  {
    "text": "Every line thrown feels more bizarre,",
    "start": 37.71,
    "end": 40.59,
    "scene": "vortex",
    "big": false
  },
  {
    "text": "Guess honesty's never part of the play.",
    "start": 40.81,
    "end": 42.85,
    "scene": "vortex",
    "big": false
  },
  {
    "text": "We go round and round…",
    "start": 43.39,
    "end": 45.35,
    "scene": "corridor",
    "big": true
  },
  {
    "text": "Drop the wrong step, end up underground…",
    "start": 47.91,
    "end": 50.67,
    "scene": "corridor",
    "big": true
  },
  {
    "text": "Gone from the map, never be found…",
    "start": 50.6,
    "end": 51.6,
    "scene": "corridor",
    "big": true
  },
  {
    "text": "Dom Shady laughs soft with a subtle rebound.",
    "start": 54.51,
    "end": 55.69,
    "scene": "corridor",
    "big": true
  },
  {
    "text": "They spotted a footprint—nah, not factual,",
    "start": 60.48,
    "end": 62.63,
    "scene": "filmnoir",
    "big": false
  },
  {
    "text": "Dom Shady's tactics stay supernatural.",
    "start": 62.54,
    "end": 65.32,
    "scene": "filmnoir",
    "big": false
  },
  {
    "text": "Hours of those shows where detectives track",
    "start": 66,
    "end": 67.89,
    "scene": "filmnoir",
    "big": false
  },
  {
    "text": "All the methods amateurs lack.",
    "start": 67.8,
    "end": 68.74,
    "scene": "filmnoir",
    "big": false
  },
  {
    "text": "Documentaries teaching what not to reveal,",
    "start": 70.72,
    "end": 73.01,
    "scene": "desk",
    "big": false
  },
  {
    "text": "How to keep every angle harder to peel.",
    "start": 72.92,
    "end": 75.92,
    "scene": "desk",
    "big": false
  },
  {
    "text": "Host says evidence always tells what's real…",
    "start": 76.32,
    "end": 78.61,
    "scene": "desk",
    "big": false
  },
  {
    "text": "Cut to me scribbling notes during every ordeal.",
    "start": 78.52,
    "end": 81.43,
    "scene": "desk",
    "big": false
  },
  {
    "text": "Neighbors whisper like they're part of a cast,",
    "start": 81.34,
    "end": 83.03,
    "scene": "glitch",
    "big": false
  },
  {
    "text": "Claiming my movement's a little too fast.",
    "start": 82.94,
    "end": 86.98,
    "scene": "glitch",
    "big": false
  },
  {
    "text": "Narrator pops in: “That theory won't last.”",
    "start": 87.03,
    "end": 91.08,
    "scene": "glitch",
    "big": false
  },
  {
    "text": "Fade to black—jump cut—back to the task.",
    "start": 91.13,
    "end": 91.65,
    "scene": "glitch",
    "big": false
  },
  {
    "text": "Dom Shady pacing like a scene on tape,",
    "start": 97.65,
    "end": 98.66,
    "scene": "vortex",
    "big": false
  },
  {
    "text": "Filling each moment with sarcastic shape.",
    "start": 98.71,
    "end": 99.71,
    "scene": "vortex",
    "big": false
  },
  {
    "text": "Drama in the room that nobody escapes,",
    "start": 99.76,
    "end": 101.44,
    "scene": "vortex",
    "big": false
  },
  {
    "text": "Nothing here follows the usual way.",
    "start": 101.37,
    "end": 103.05,
    "scene": "vortex",
    "big": false
  },
  {
    "text": "We go round and round…",
    "start": 102.98,
    "end": 106.26,
    "scene": "corridor",
    "big": true
  },
  {
    "text": "Drop the wrong step, end up underground…",
    "start": 106.82,
    "end": 109.54,
    "scene": "corridor",
    "big": true
  },
  {
    "text": "Gone from the map, never be found…",
    "start": 110.3,
    "end": 113.45,
    "scene": "corridor",
    "big": true
  },
  {
    "text": "Dom Shady hums low with a playful sound.",
    "start": 113.36,
    "end": 120.89,
    "scene": "corridor",
    "big": true
  },
  {
    "text": "Every thought loops back like a hallway bend,",
    "start": 120.8,
    "end": 124.13,
    "scene": "bridge",
    "big": false
  },
  {
    "text": "Every claim they toss twists without an end.",
    "start": 124.04,
    "end": 127.01,
    "scene": "bridge",
    "big": false
  },
  {
    "text": "Rumors bounce wild—none of them blend,",
    "start": 126.92,
    "end": 129.57,
    "scene": "bridge",
    "big": false
  },
  {
    "text": "Dom Shady just wants the script to amend.",
    "start": 129.48,
    "end": 132.24,
    "scene": "bridge",
    "big": false
  },
  {
    "text": "Camera pans out on a crooked grin,",
    "start": 132.56,
    "end": 135.22,
    "scene": "outro",
    "big": false
  },
  {
    "text": "Pen hits paper like trouble's twin.",
    "start": 135.4,
    "end": 137.96,
    "scene": "outro",
    "big": false
  },
  {
    "text": "Story keeps spinning from within,",
    "start": 138.12,
